TITLE: Synchronous Testing in Mocha
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to write tests for synchronous code where no callback or Promise handling is needed.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mochajs/mocha/blob/main/docs-next/src/content/docs/features/asynchronous-code.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
describe("Array", function () {
  describe("#indexOf()", function () {
    it("should return -1 when the value is not present", function () {
      [1, 2, 3].indexOf(5).should.equal(-1);
      [1, 2, 3].indexOf(0).should.equal(-1);
    });
  });
});
```

