TITLE: Synchronous Testing in Mocha
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to write synchronous tests without callbacks, using Array indexOf as an example
SOURCE: https://github.com/mochajs/mocha/blob/main/docs/index.md#2025-04-22_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
describe('Array', function () {
  describe('#indexOf()', function () {
    it('should return -1 when the value is not present', function () {
      [1, 2, 3].indexOf(5).should.equal(-1);
      [1, 2, 3].indexOf(0).should.equal(-1);
