TITLE: Mocha Hooks Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Shows the implementation of before, after, beforeEach, and afterEach hooks for test setup and cleanup
SOURCE: https://github.com/mochajs/mocha/blob/main/docs/index.md#2025-04-22_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
describe('hooks', function () {
  before(function () {
    // runs once before the first test in this block
  });

  after(function () {
    // runs once after the last test in this block
  });

  beforeEach(function () {
    // runs before each test in this block
  });

  afterEach(function () {
    // runs after each test in this block
  });

  // test cases
});
```

