TITLE: Async/Await Testing in Mocha
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates using async/await syntax for asynchronous testing, showing both setup hooks and test cases
SOURCE: https://github.com/mochajs/mocha/blob/main/docs/index.md#2025-04-22_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
beforeEach(async function () {
