TITLE: Promise-based Testing in Mocha
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to test Promise-based APIs using Mocha and Chai as Promised for assertions. Shows setup with beforeEach and testing with Promise returns.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mochajs/mocha/blob/main/docs-next/src/content/docs/features/asynchronous-code.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_2

