TITLE: Simplified Asynchronous Testing with done() in Mocha
DESCRIPTION: Simplified example of an asynchronous test using the done() callback directly.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mochajs/mocha/blob/main/docs/index.md#2025-04-22_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
describe('User', function () {
  describe('#save()', function () {
    it('should save without error', function (done) {
      var user = new User('Luna');
      user.save(done);
    });
  });
});
```

