TITLE: Asynchronous Testing with Callbacks in Mocha
DESCRIPTION: Example of writing an asynchronous test in Mocha using a callback function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mochajs/mocha/blob/main/docs/index.md#2025-04-22_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
describe('User', function () {
  describe('#save()', function () {
    it('should save without error', function (done) {
      var user = new User('Luna');
      user.save(function (err) {
        if (err) done(err);
        else done();
      });
    });
  });
});
```

